---
const primary   = "#252e67";
const accent    = "#f5a71c";
const secondary = "#a91e23";
const neutral   = "#4a5072";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Grand Lodge History – Oregon Knights of Pythias</title>
  <meta name="description" content="History of the Grand Domain of Oregon, Knights of Pythias." />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <style define:vars={{ primary, accent, secondary, neutral }}>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root { --max-w: 67vw; --font: 'Trebuchet MS', Trebuchet, 'Gill Sans MT', Arial, sans-serif; }
    body { font-family: var(--font); color: #1a1a2e; line-height: 1.7;
      background-image: url('/mainbg.png'); background-size: cover;
      background-position: center; background-attachment: fixed;
      background-color: var(--primary); }
    a { color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    .tricolor { display: flex; height: 5px; border-top: 2px solid #000; border-bottom: 2px solid #000; }
    .tricolor span { flex: 1; }

    header { background: #a91e23; color: #fff; padding: 0 1.5rem; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; }
    .header-inner { max-width: var(--max-w); margin: 0 auto; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem; padding: .5rem 0; }
    .brand-name { font-size: .95rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .04em; -webkit-text-stroke: .3px var(--primary); paint-order: stroke fill; }
    .brand-sub  { font-size: .65rem; color: #fff; opacity: .92; }
    .header-logo { height: 44px; width: auto; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .brand-group { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .5rem; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: .4rem; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .motto { font-size: .72rem; color: var(--accent); font-style: italic; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .03em; }
    .ext-link { color: var(--accent); font-size: .75rem; padding: .2rem .4rem; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3); font-weight: 600; }
    .ext-link:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,.15); text-decoration: none; }
    .ext-link.active { background: var(--primary); color: #fff; border-color: var(--primary); font-weight: 600; pointer-events: none; }

    main { max-width: 860px; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 1.5rem;
      background: rgba(222,211,195,0.90); border-radius: 6px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.18); }
    .breadcrumb { font-size: .8rem; color: #888; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .breadcrumb a { color: var(--primary); }
    h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; color: var(--primary); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .04em;
      border-bottom: 3px solid var(--accent); padding-bottom: .35rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--primary); margin: 1.5rem 0 .5rem; }
    p { margin-bottom: .9rem; font-size: .95rem; color: #333; }
    .stub-notice { background: #fff8e1; border: 1px solid #ffe082; border-radius: 6px;
      padding: .75rem 1rem; font-size: .88rem; color: #6d4c00; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .timeline { border-left: 3px solid var(--accent); padding-left: 1.25rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
    .timeline-item { margin-bottom: 1.25rem; position: relative; }
    .timeline-item::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: -1.45rem; top: .35rem;
      width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent); }
    .timeline-item .year { font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary); font-size: .9rem; }
    .timeline-item .event { font-size: .9rem; color: #444; }

    footer { background: var(--secondary); color: var(--accent); text-align: center;
      padding: 1rem; margin-top: 2rem; font-size: .82rem;
      position: sticky; bottom: 0; z-index: 100; }
    footer a { color: var(--accent); opacity: .85; }
    footer a:hover { opacity: 1; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="tricolor">
    <span style={`background:${primary}`}></span>
    <span style={`background:${secondary}`}></span>
    <span style={`background:${accent}`}></span>
  </div>
  <header>
    <div class="header-inner">
      <a href="/" style="text-decoration:none" class="brand-group">
        <img src="/seal.png" alt="KoP Seal" class="header-logo" />
        <div>
          <div class="brand-name">Oregon Knights of Pythias</div>
          <div class="brand-sub">Grand Domain of Oregon</div>
          <div class="motto">Friendship &middot; Charity &middot; Benevolence</div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <nav class="nav-links">
        <a href="/" class="ext-link">Home</a>
        <a href="/grand-lodge/officers" class="ext-link">Grand Officers</a>
        <a href="/grand-lodge/history" class="ext-link active">History</a>
        <a href="https://www.pythias.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="ext-link">Supreme Lodge ↗</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="tricolor">
    <span style={`background:${primary}`}></span>
    <span style={`background:${secondary}`}></span>
    <span style={`background:${accent}`}></span>
  </div>

  <main>
    <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">← Lodge Directory</a></div>
    <h1>Grand Lodge History</h1>

    <div class="stub-notice">
      This page is a placeholder. Detailed Grand Lodge history will be added here.
    </div>

    <p>
      The Knights of Pythias was founded on February 19, 1864 by Justus H. Rathbone in Washington, D.C.
      It was the first fraternal organization to receive a charter under an Act of Congress.
      The order's motto — <em>Friendship, Charity, Benevolence</em> — has guided its members for over 160 years.
    </p>

    <h2>The Grand Domain of Oregon</h2>
    <p>
      Oregon lodges have been part of the Knights of Pythias since the late 19th century, bringing the order's
      ideals of brotherhood and service to communities across the state. The Grand Domain of Oregon
      oversees all subordinate lodges within the state.
    </p>

    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="year">1864</div>
        <div class="event">Knights of Pythias founded in Washington, D.C. by Justus H. Rathbone.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="year">1868</div>
        <div class="event">Supreme Lodge established; order expands nationally.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="year">Late 1800s</div>
        <div class="event">Oregon lodges chartered; Grand Domain of Oregon established.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="year">Present</div>
        <div class="event">Oregon lodges continue to serve their communities through Friendship, Charity, and Benevolence.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Grand Domain of Oregon &mdash; Knights of Pythias &middot;
      <a href="https://www.pythias.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">pythias.org</a>
      <span style="margin-left:.5rem"><a href="/admin">Admin</a></span>
    </p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
